{CHARACTER_NAME}: PERCY
{DIALOGUE}: I think of it as a bucket of piss to drown rats in.
{DIALOGUE}: That's all.
{META_DATA}: (scans their faces)
{DIALOGUE}: Anybody doesn't like it can kiss my ass.
{DIALOGUE}: How's that sit?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal steps forward, wanting to slug the little bastard.
