{CHARACTER_NAME}: DEL
{DIALOGUE}: Oh.
{DIALOGUE}: Oh my.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul arrives at Coffey's cell.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Coffey's on his bunk facing the wall.
