{DIALOGUE}: C'mon, fuckstick.
{DIALOGUE}: No sneakin' up on me this time.
{DIALOGUE}: We'll go man to man, see who's the better fel--
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal unlocks the cell--and sidesteps, revealing Harry pointing a fire hose.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The hose erupts, driving Billy across the cell with bone-jarring force.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They batter him half- senseless, then cut the water.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy collapses in a heap.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul and Brutal drag him semi-conscious from his cell and get the straitjacket on him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He comes around as they draw the straps tight and pull him to his feet.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: C'mon, Wild Bill.
{DIALOGUE}: Little walky walky.
