{DIALOGUE}: He was just a bushwackin' John Law!
{DIALOGUE}: Dumb sonovabitch sat with his back to the door and kilt by a drunk!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{DIALOGUE}: Oh, my suds and body!
{DIALOGUE}: A history lesson!
{DIALOGUE}: You just never know what you're gonna get when you come to work everyday on the Green Mile.
{DIALOGUE}: Thank you, Wild Bill.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy lets out a scream of rage and throws himself at Brutal.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal, bored, shoves him back toward Paul, who then propels him down the Mile toward the open restraint room door.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy sees where they intend to put him, resorts to pleading:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Oh, not in there!
{DIALOGUE}: C'mon now, I'll be good!
{DIALOGUE}: Honest Injun I will!
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{DIALOGUE}: No!
{DIALOGUE}: Ummmmhhhh...urg...ah!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He suddenly drops to the floor, bucking and jerking wildly, spewing drool.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Harry's eyes go wide.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HARRY
{DIALOGUE}: Holy Christ, he's pitchin' a fit!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul reaches down and unceremoniously starts dragging Billy kicking and writhing the rest of the way.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: He'll be fine, boys.
{DIALOGUE}: Trust me on this one.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal helps Paul toss Billy headlong into the padded room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They slam the door...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: RESTRAINT ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and Billy staggers to his feet in the straitjacket, inarticulate with rage, starts throwing himself against the door, screaming at the top of his lungs.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: ALL I WANTED ME WAS A LITTLE CORNBREAD, YOU MUTHERFUCKERS!
{META_DATA}: FADE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. E BLOCK - NEXT DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul and Brutal unlock the restraint room.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy looks up from the corner, pale and drained.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Softly:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: I learnt my lesson.
{DIALOGUE}: I'll be good.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. E BLOCK - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy's back in his cell, quiet for a change.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toot-Toot is outside the bars, mopping the floor.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy notices a chocolate Moon Pie in Toot's shirt pocket.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Pssss.
{DIALOGUE}: Hey.
{DIALOGUE}: Give'ya nickel for that Moon Pie.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toot looks around.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Nobody's watching, and a nickel's a nickel.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He steps to Billy's bars, swaps the Moon Pie for the money.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toot hurries away.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy unwraps the Moon Pie, makes sure he's not being watched...and crams the entire thing into his mouth...
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and here comes Brutal strolling down the Mile, doing a cell check and jotting on a clipboard.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pauses, seeing:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy at his bars.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just standing there staring.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His cheeks bulging way out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal steps closer, fascinated...what the fuck is that.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy waits until he's just a bit closer--
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: --and he slams his fists against his own cheeks, propelling a disgusting spew of liquefied chocolate sludge into Brutal's face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy falls back onto his bunk, shrieking with laughter:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Li'l Black Sambo, yassuh, boss, yassuh, howdoo you do?
