{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal leads Del up the Mile, Paul and the others at their heels.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Percy's at the duty desk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He smirks and rolls his eyes as Del goes by.
