{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. E BLOCK - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and they're still chatting a short time later, waiting for Del's return.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Percy actually looks happy for a change, feeling genuinely accepted for the first time...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Billy is watching from his cell.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just watching.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The door opens.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del returns with Mr. Jingles on his shoulder, escorted by Brutal.
