{DIALOGUE}: They love Mr. Jingles!
{DIALOGUE}: They laugh and cheer and clap they hands!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PERCY
{DIALOGUE}: Well, that's just aces.
{DIALOGUE}: Pop back in your cell, old-timer.
