{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del gives him a look of almost comical mistrust...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and the old Percy comes back.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He bares his teeth in a mock snarl and curls his fingers as if to grab Del.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's a joke, but Del doesn't know that--he jerks back in fear and trips over Brutal's big feet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del goes down hard, hitting the linoleum with the back of his head.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mr. Jingles jumps clear, goes squeaking down the Mile.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del sits up, painfully clutching his head.
