{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: Ain't you sweet.
{DIALOGUE}: Soft.
{DIALOGUE}: Like a girl.
{DIALOGUE}: I druther fuck your asshole than your sister's pussy, I think.
