{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: Wharton!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and Billy lets go, stepping back with his hands raised, laughing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Percy darts across the Mile in terror and cringes against the cell opposite, breathing so loud and fast it almost sounds like sobbing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{DIALOGUE}: I let 'im go, I'us just playin' and I let 'im go!
{DIALOGUE}: Never hurt a hair on his purty head!
{META_DATA}: (grins at Percy)
{DIALOGUE}: Your noodle ain't limp at all, loverboy!
{DIALOGUE}: I think you sweet on ol' Billy the Kid...
{META_DATA}: (sniffs his fingers)
{DIALOGUE}: ...oooh, but smell you.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Down at his cell, Del starts laughing shrilly.
