{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del is throwing the spool.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Mr. Jingles is fetching it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The silence is thick.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Just the clack-clatter of the spool, and the skitter skitter of tiny mouse paws on concrete.
