{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His old enemy Percy.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{DIALOGUE}: Percy, no!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Percy stomps the heel of his heavy work shoe down on Mr. Jingles.
