{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Up at the duty desk, Dean and Harry get up from a cribbage game, stunned and furious.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Percy strolls past, exits to the execution chamber.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Del is still screaming, all his pent-up terror and grief pouring out at the dying mouse.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And then comes a soft, urgent voice:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COFFEY
{DIALOGUE}: Give'm to me.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They turn.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Coffey's got his arms out through his bars, one massive hand spread open.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COFFEY
{DIALOGUE}: Give'm to me.
{DIALOGUE}: Might still be time.
