{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Splintered bones are poking at the hide.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{DIALOGUE}: What are you doing?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul doesn't answer, just lays Mr. Jingles into Coffey's hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Coffey pulls the mouse in through his bars and lays his other hand gently over it, cupping the creature.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All we see now is the tail hanging out the side, twitching weakly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{DIALOGUE}: Paul, what the hell--
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul motions him quiet.
