{CHARACTER_NAME}: DEL
{DIALOGUE}: Please, John.
{DIALOGUE}: Oh Johnny, help him, please help him, s'il vous plait.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Harry and Dean join the group.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Everybody watching now.
