{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{META_DATA}: (softly)
{DIALOGUE}: Oh, dear Jesus.
{DIALOGUE}: The tail.
{DIALOGUE}: Look at the tail.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They do.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The tail is no longer weak and dying.
