{DIALOGUE}: Jesus Christ, three witnesses puked all over the floor up there!
{DIALOGUE}: And the smell!
{DIALOGUE}: I got Van Hay to open both doors, but that smell won't come out for five damn years, that's what I'm betting!
{DIALOGUE}: And that asshole Wharton is singing about it!
{DIALOGUE}: I can hear him!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{META_DATA}: (quietly)
{DIALOGUE}: Can he carry a tune, Hal?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: This pulls the plug on the moment--Hal snorts, triggering laughter among the men, a wild release of tension and fear.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Everybody starts feeling a bit saner again as it dies down:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAL
{DIALOGUE}: Okay, boys.
{DIALOGUE}: Okay.
{DIALOGUE}: Now what the hell happened?
