{DIALOGUE}: Have that transfer request on my desk first thing.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hal heads back up the stairs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Brutal shoves Percy aside and wheels Delacroix's body down the tunnel.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. E BLOCK - NIGHT
