{DIALOGUE}: Me too.
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. PAUL'S HOUSE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul enters in darkness, hangs his hat.
