{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SOFT MUSIC BEGINS: Gene Austin singing "Did You Ever See A Dream Walking?"
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He pours a drink at the kitchen table, takes a sip, lays the glass down.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jan sleepily appears from the darkness behind him, entering the kitchen.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He realizes she's there, glances back.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She can sense the weight on his soul.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She comes to him, folds his head into her arms.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They stand that way, he drawing strength and she giving it, as the music plays on...
