{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. BACKYARD - MORNING
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ...and they walk outside to find MELINDA MOORES sitting in the sun, frail and wasted, a blanket on her knees.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She'd be beautiful if not for the cancer killing her.
