{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul softly interjects:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: You saw what he did with the mouse.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: This stops everybody cold.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dean puts his chicken down, wipes his hands.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looks are traded in the silence.
