{DIALOGUE}: Hold on now.
{DIALOGUE}: You're talking about our jobs.
{DIALOGUE}: Sneak a sick woman onto a cellblock?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: Hal would never allow that.
{DIALOGUE}: You know him, he wouldn't believe something unless it fell on him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BRUTAL
{DIALOGUE}: So you're talking about taking John Coffey to her.
{DIALOGUE}: That's more than just our jobs, Paul.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DEAN
{DIALOGUE}: Damn right.
