{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The men gasp, shocked to see Billy on his feet, grinning and weaving like a punch-drunk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Coffey's reaction is beyond simple surprise; he's actually trembling at Billy's touch as if some electrical circuit were engaged.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: His eyes are wide and horrified, as if he'd just put his hand in a basket full of snakes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He tries to pull away, but Billy has him tight, that mysterious circuit blazing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BILLY
{META_DATA}: (slurring wildly)
{DIALOGUE}: Where you fink you're goin'?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Coffey responds softly, with utmost horror:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COFFEY
{DIALOGUE}: You're a bad man.
