{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. MOORES HOUSE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Headlights come over the rise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The truck appears, rumbling down toward the house.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The world is isolated and still.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IN THE TRUCK CAB
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Harry stops and cuts the engine, leaving the headlights on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Silence now, save for the trilling of crickets.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: IN THE STAKEBED
