{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAL
{DIALOGUE}: Who the hell goes there at two- thirty in the goddamn morning?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: Hal, it's us!
{DIALOGUE}: It's Paul and Brutal--it's us!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The door swings wider, revealing Hal's face gaunt and haggard in the yellow porch light, stunned to see them:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAL
{DIALOGUE}: Paul, what are you doing here at this hour?
{DIALOGUE}: Jesus, it's not a lockdown, is it?
{DIALOGUE}: Or a riot?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PAUL
{DIALOGUE}: Hal, God's sakes, take your finger off the trigger...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hal doesn't, aiming past them at the truck in the yard.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAL
{DIALOGUE}: Are you hostages?
{DIALOGUE}: Who's out there?
{DIALOGUE}: Who's by that truck?
