{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A whisper:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COFFEY
{DIALOGUE}: My hand.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Paul can't help it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He has to.
